  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Published in 2021 by Leuven University Press, \"Evolving as a Digital Scholar\" addresses the contemporary transitions and methodologies within digital scholarship. Although currently, it has not garnered explicit citation or online discourse, it remains supported by commercial platforms such as Amazon and Goodreads, indicating its accessibility to broader audiences.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The work titled \"Evolving as a Digital Scholar,\" released in 2021, highlights crucial transformations within the realms of digital scholarship. This publication, stewarded by Leuven University Press, serves as a resource aiming to bridge traditional academic practices with the evolving demands of online scholarship. While it currently has no citation metrics or community discussions to report, the presence of the book on commercial platforms such as Amazon and Goodreads signals its potential reach and relevance.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">One notable aspect of this work is its inferred role concerning policy sustainability, demonstrated by the existence of links to one Sustainable Development Goal (SDG). This connection suggests that the content may hold significant implications relevant to ongoing policy discussions in the digital arena. Although it has yet to achieve widespread academic uptake, reflected by a citation count of two, this initial engagement may serve as a foundation for future scholarly dialogue.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">The lack of engagement on high-fidelity social platforms such as Wikipedia, Reddit, and Bluesky signifies that \"Evolving as a Digital Scholar\" has yet to penetrate broader public discourse. Nonetheless, its accessibility through notable commercial outlets indicates a potential audience that transcends traditional academic boundaries, possibly encouraging interdisciplinary exploration of digital scholarship.</p>\n\n<p class=\"story-text\">As the landscape of academic publishing continues to evolve, works such as this one could play pivotal roles in redefining scholarly practices. Continued monitoring of its citations and public interactions will be essential in assessing its influence and impact as digital scholarship becomes increasingly vital across various disciplines.</p>",
